&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/CHICAGO-CUVEE-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8384&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/CHICAGO-CUVEE-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;CHICAGO- CUVEE- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;59&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One of the most exquisite spaces in Chicago, &lt;strong&gt;Cuv&eacute;e&lt;/strong&gt; is an intimate lounge that focuses on champagne. From a private alley entrance, an elegant clientele enters the space to a unique setting where seating is in the center of the room rather than along the perimeter. An extensive list of champagnes by the glass or bottle, champagne cocktails, and even large format bottles are just part of the appeal. Bottle service compromises a full selection of top brands as well as a cocktail list. Dress to Impress.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please visit&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.CuveeChicago.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;CUVEE&amp;#8217;s website&lt;/a&gt;,&nbsp;contact &lt;strong&gt;Cuv&eacute;e&lt;/strong&gt; by phone at +1-312-202-9221&nbsp;or email at &lt;u&gt;info@CuveeChicago&nbsp;&lt;/u&gt;to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of both male and female guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the nightclub by phone or email 24 hours prior to your arrival date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 4 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife Access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

